original: Mommy intended to cook but encountered a setback when she found the refrigerator broken. Unable to retrieve any ingredients, Daddy intervened, successfully repairing the refrigerator with a tool. With the refrigerator fixed, Mommy prepared a delightful dinner for the family, resulting in a joyous and satisfying meal that brought happiness to all.
